com.android.car.internal

注释类型 ExcludeFromCodeCoverageGeneratedReport


  • @Target(value={TYPE,CONSTRUCTOR,METHOD})
public @interface ExcludeFromCodeCoverageGeneratedReport
    Annotation used to mark code to be excluded from coverage report.

    • 元素详细资料

      • reason

        public abstract int reason
        The reason explaining why the code is being excluded from the code coverage report.

        Possible reasons to exclude code from coverage report are:

        • DEPRECATED_CODE to exclude deprecated code from coverage report
        • BOILERPLATE_CODE to exclude boilerplate code like Object methods, android.os.Parcel methods, etc
        • DUMP_INFO to exclude dump info methods
        • DEBUGGING_CODE to exclude debugging
        • PRIVATE_CONSTRUCTOR to exclude private constructors from classes that only provide static methods purpose code

      • details

        public abstract java.lang.String details
        Optional field used to provide extra details about the excluded code (e.g. it can be used to tag a follow up bug).
        默认值:
        ""
